These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-1::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, prince
There 2 different types of food: kiwi, lemon
1. the prince-smoker is on the left or right of the cain-smoker##3
2. the person eating lemon is on the right of the prince-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2   |
| Cigar   | prince  | cain |
| Food       | kiwi | lemon |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-2::.
2 different games are played: whist, domino
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: golf, surfing
1. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left or right of the person playing domino##3
2. the person playing domino is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2   |
| Game   | whist | domino |
| Sport      | surfing     | golf  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-3::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: taxi, scooter
There are 2 different nationalities: french, nigerian
1. the french is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
2. the french is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Transport   | taxi | scooter  |
| Nationality   | french | nigerian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-4::.
City: colone, hamburg
There 2 different types of food: apricot, tomato
1. the person eating apricot is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
2. the person traveling to colone is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |
| City   | hamburg | colone   |
| Food       | tomato | apricot |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-5::.
House: farmhouse, colonial
There are 2 different nationalities: american, australian
1. the australian is on the right of the colonial house##1
2. the colonial house is on the left or right of the farmhouse house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |
| House   | colonial    | farmhouse    |
| Nationality   | american | australian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-6::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: ambient, d&b
The people have 2 different hobbies: dancing, rock-climbing
1. the fan of ambient is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##3
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |
| Music-Genre   | ambient   | d&b     |
| Hobby   | dancing | rock-climbing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-7::.
