2 different pets are kept: cat, snake
1. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the fan of funk##3
2. the owner of the snake is on the left of the fan of salsa##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |  2   |
| Music-Genre   | funk | salsa |
| Pet           | snake     | cat  |

